"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-andy-murray-news-tennis-paris-olympics-2024-b1172797.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Andy Murrayhas confirmed his professional singles career is over after pulling out of the draw for theOlympicGames in Paris.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0671803367171314e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray withdrew from his last singles match against Jordan Thompson in the early stages of the first set at Queen's Club last month with a back problem andmissed the subsequent singles at Wimbledon.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.889442989814773e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Thompson_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9920171090555051, \"rank\": 0.0037318405970944053, \"text\": \"Jordan Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Thompson_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Thompson_(tennis)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had been hopeful of doubling up in both the singles and doubles at these Games but today confirmed he would not be in the draw for the singles.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, the 37-year-old will solely turn his focus to the men's doubles where he is playing alongside Dan Evans with the British pair drawn to face Japanese duo Taro Daniel and Kei Nishikori in the opening round.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.997803650115343, \"rank\": 0.002201184452072526, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9951381504576972, \"rank\": 0.0047766487295380945, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.8505240376653479, \"rank\": 0.12072401893585277, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taro Daniel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\"}, {\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kei Nishikori\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Announcing his decision to forego that format, he said: \\\"I have taken the decision to withdraw from the singles to concentrate on the doubles with Dan.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our practice has been great and we are playing well together.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Really looking forward to getting started and representing GB one more time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9959793107779414, \"rank\": 0.00403538684196501, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both Murray and Evans have had their own injury issues in the lengthy build-up to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.889442989814773e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999997053237, \"rank\": 2.9459812005838514e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 Olympic Games tennis schedule in full: Events, UK start times and dates  Two-time Olympic singles champion Murray pulled out of the singles at Wimbledon after losing his race to be fit in time following surgery on a cyst on his back.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9927772144703652, \"rank\": 0.0072753335344926656, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.889442989814773e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he still entered the men's doubles and played with brother Jamie, the pair losing in the opening roundbefore an emotional on-court farewell at a tournament where he was a two-time former champion.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evans, meanwhile, slipped and injured his knee at Queen's and then struggled at the All England Club where he lost in the opening round, later complaining that he had been playing on one knee.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_England_Lawn_Tennis_and_Croquet_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"All England Club\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_England_Lawn_Tennis_and_Croquet_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_England_Lawn_Tennis_and_Croquet_Club\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evans and Murray are both accomplished doubles players and have been given a clean bill of health to compete in that format.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.889442989814773e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Novak Djokovic and Rafael Nadal are on course to meet each other in a mouth-watering clash in the second round of the men's singles.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 2122, \"end\": 2134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the British men in the singles, Jack Draper will face Nishikori, Cameron Norrie takes on Tallon Griekspoor - with Carlos Alcaraz potentially lying in wait in round two, and Evans drawn against Moez Echargui.\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2244, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9951381504576972, \"rank\": 0.0047766487295380945, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9926967693033829, \"rank\": 0.007352941176469691, \"text\": \"Jack Draper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\"}, {\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_Norrie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cameron Norrie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_Norrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_Norrie\"}, {\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 2413, \"end\": 2418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999997053237, \"rank\": 2.9459812005838514e-10, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 2433, \"end\": 2446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moez_Echargui\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moez Echargui\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\